summary:
Hereby is the summary of my technical and soft skills based on one of the feedbacks given by a team leader and senior manager at PwC (references and official feedback are available upon request):

Great sense of professional skepticism, eagerness for new knowledge and ability to learn quickly, high attention to details – all these allow me quickly to assimilate into a new team, learn new legislation, and start coordinating the delivery on absolutely new clients very quickly. I demonstrate excellent planning and time management skills, and the ability to manage the team and deliver a high-quality product. 

I am a high committed person, with maturity and willingness to take on new clients / participate in new projects. Excellent team player and have strong people management skills. Having a natural sense of tactfulness in conjunction with knowledge of the company's procedures allows me to be a great coach for peers or junior colleagues.
